('Thank you Website Dummy Properties and Alissa for making my dreams come true and still working behind the scenes in every capacity to knit all the tiny pieces together from home warranties to transfer of services. I couldn''t be happier that I chose your company and Alissa to work with!', 'Kimberly Davenport', 'Alissa Meriwether', false, 2),
('Professional, friendly, courteous, good follow up, thorough, and competent... Alissa is our agent of choice!', 'Aletha Marcum', 'Alissa Meriwether', false, 3),
